            <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 4 月 28 日消息，博主 @数码闲聊站近日曝光了&nbsp;OPPO Pad 3&nbsp;平板电脑，这款平板电脑据称采用 3K&nbsp;分辨率面板，<span class="accentTextColor">配备高通骁龙&nbsp;8 Gen 3&nbsp;处理器及&nbsp;16GB RAM</span>，同时可选“智能触控键盘”<span class="accentTextColor"></span>。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="352" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/4/716f75f3-73c7-4696-9ed7-7da7e66d2658.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xYy9xYzEwOC5wbmc=,t_100,g_3,y_11,x_11,a_0/format,f_auto" title="OPPO Pad 3 平板电脑搭载 3K 分辨率面板，配骁龙 8 Gen 3 + 16GB RAM" width="700" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="352" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/4/be77e82c-1354-4a4b-b0ba-bd1b3dc7c482.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xYy9xYzEwOC5wbmc=,t_100,g_3,y_11,x_11,a_0/format,f_auto" title="OPPO Pad 3 平板电脑搭载 3K 分辨率面板，配骁龙 8 Gen 3 + 16GB RAM" width="700" /></p><p>据IT之家此前报道，OPPO Pad 2&nbsp;发布于&nbsp;2023&nbsp;年&nbsp;3&nbsp;月，这款平板采用一块&nbsp;11.61&nbsp;英寸&nbsp;2800×2000 LCD&nbsp;屏幕，<span class="accentTextColor">搭载联发科天玑&nbsp;9000&nbsp;移动平台</span>，辅以&nbsp;LPDDR5 RAM + UFS 3.1&nbsp;闪存，8GB+256GB&nbsp;版售价&nbsp;2999&nbsp;元、12GB+256GB&nbsp;版售价&nbsp;3399&nbsp;元、12+512GB&nbsp;版售价&nbsp;3999&nbsp;元。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="820" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/3/036fe969-4e76-457a-a0a6-e2663b68232c.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="OPPO Pad 3 平板电脑搭载 3K 分辨率面板，配骁龙 8 Gen 3 + 16GB RAM" width="1440" /></p><p style="text-align: left;">相关阅读：</p><p class="ad-tips">广告声明：文内含有的对外跳转链接（包括不限于超链接、二维码、口令等形式），用于传递更多信息，节省甄选时间，结果仅供参考，IT之家所有文章均包含本声明。</p>
